{
  "id": "3137878607",
  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"16lmz9-L\">为了能好好回答这个问题，我特地查了很多资料给你找来几种多数为男性患者的严重疾病：</p><p data-pid=\"Yc6IQLTd\"><b>1、X连锁肩胛腓骨肌病，关联基因FHL1，XL遗传方式</b></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-252e1bda6043bbaf1cb08e6761f57438_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"637\" data-rawheight=\"475\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-9dae1bfec13f0085d118614f8f75ca6b\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-db34a7409da5d39e2340b9ab6376f7b6_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"637\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-252e1bda6043bbaf1cb08e6761f57438_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-252e1bda6043bbaf1cb08e6761f57438_720w.webp?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"637\" data-rawheight=\"475\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-9dae1bfec13f0085d118614f8f75ca6b\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-db34a7409da5d39e2340b9ab6376f7b6_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"637\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-252e1bda6043bbaf1cb08e6761f57438_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-252e1bda6043bbaf1cb08e6761f57438_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" height=\"475\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></div><figcaption>依靠轮椅生活</figcaption></figure><p data-pid=\"NlRJsmko\">X连锁肩胛腓骨肌病是一种进行性肌病，临床表现为<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=600608634&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E8%82%8C%E6%97%A0%E5%8A%9B&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">进行性肌无力<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>和萎缩、上下肢无力、足下垂、<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=600608634&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%BF%BC%E7%8A%B6%E8%82%A9%E8%83%9B&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">翼状肩胛<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，肌肉活检可见肌病病变。<b>大部分患者失去独立行走能力，必须依靠轮椅生活。</b></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4b4e6578dc41aa4b6bb6451d57bd3c2e_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1195\" data-rawheight=\"713\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-d9aaffb9b11a16f2b9b6f34935c16c63\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5ad5d9fbaff773e856c63e03110f29a0_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1195\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-4b4e6578dc41aa4b6bb6451d57bd3c2e_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-4b4e6578dc41aa4b6bb6451d57bd3c2e_720w.webp?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1195\" data-rawheight=\"713\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-d9aaffb9b11a16f2b9b6f34935c16c63\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5ad5d9fbaff773e856c63e03110f29a0_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1195\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-4b4e6578dc41aa4b6bb6451d57bd3c2e_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4b4e6578dc41aa4b6bb6451d57bd3c2e_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" height=\"713\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></div><figcaption>部分突变位点</figcaption></figure><p data-pid=\"S_mzi4IU\"><b>2、X连锁原卟啉病，关联基因ALAS2，XL遗传</b></p><p data-pid=\"93FVEpUM\">X连锁原卟啉病（XLP）是一种X连锁遗传的<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=600608634&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=3&amp;q=%E5%8D%9F%E5%95%89%E7%97%85&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">卟啉病<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，男性患者的临床表现为皮肤光敏感性，通常从婴儿期或幼儿期开始发病。</p><p data-pid=\"xhrR6VOu\">患者在光照下几分钟就会感到皮肤刺痛、火辣、疼痛以及瘙痒，并可能伴有发红、肿胀。光毒性反应引起的疼痛可能与皮肤损伤不成比例，并可能持续数小时甚至数天。<b>患者的<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=600608634&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=2&amp;q=%E5%85%89%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F%E6%80%A7&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">光敏感性<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>可能终身存在。</b></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-772fed3a2d565938fe7fc34bb132719e_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1181\" data-rawheight=\"817\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-c9ba95eb8d2feb51d1bbb429d84a50db\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6425f8e399a5b2f85cd5a80741c2baa0_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1181\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-772fed3a2d565938fe7fc34bb132719e_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1181' height='817'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"1181\" data-rawheight=\"817\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-c9ba95eb8d2feb51d1bbb429d84a50db\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-6425f8e399a5b2f85cd5a80741c2baa0_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1181\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-772fed3a2d565938fe7fc34bb132719e_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-772fed3a2d565938fe7fc34bb132719e_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div><figcaption>部分突变位点</figcaption></figure><p data-pid=\"-lZuVSmJ\">急性光敏性的反复发作可能会导致暴露光照下的皮肤发生慢性病变（<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=600608634&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E8%8B%94%E7%99%A3%E5%8C%96&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">苔癣化<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>、类革假囊泡、嘴唇周围开槽）以及指甲中的半月消失。XLP患者中出现肝疾病的比例未知，但只要没有严重的肝疾病，患者的预期寿命就不会缩短。女性携带者的表型不一，轻者无症状，重者与男性患者的症状无异。</p><p data-pid=\"zAcWFT65\"><b>3、α地贫伴X连锁智力障碍综合征，关联基因ATRX，XL遗传方式</b></p><p data-pid=\"tjFOZzAJ\">α地中海贫血性智力障碍也叫ATR-X综合征，是一种以显著的颅面特征、生殖器异常、严重精神发育迟缓、张力减退、<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=600608634&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=3&amp;q=%E6%99%BA%E5%8A%9B%E9%9A%9C%E7%A2%8D&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">智力障碍<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>并伴轻度到中度α-地中海贫血性的X连锁遗传性疾病。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-f135273725162951d2d08fad98bd8cdf_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"249\" data-rawheight=\"436\" data-size=\"small\" data-original-token=\"v2-cd2593f5e4b9acc1c5871c248b43be55\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-84acd2c5ebe4f812ea855a332a7ebcad_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"249\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='249' height='436'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"249\" data-rawheight=\"436\" data-size=\"small\" data-original-token=\"v2-cd2593f5e4b9acc1c5871c248b43be55\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-84acd2c5ebe4f812ea855a332a7ebcad_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"249\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-f135273725162951d2d08fad98bd8cdf_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"Wch-bOKd\">颅面特征包括头围小、内眦距过宽或眼距过宽、小鼻、帐篷形上唇、下唇突出或外翻、粗糙面容。婴儿期发育迟缓和受累者不能独立走路或说话。<b>在男性中外显率推测为100%，因为ATRX的突变还未在正常男性中被报道过</b>。目前没有发病率相关的统计数据。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-73479bd410a825131ce793eadfa4ae04_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1183\" data-rawheight=\"767\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-99068679309ad3dcb226ec1d1c55865a\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b1e2b5f140b1b0eca2932b0ac8c90d2b_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1183\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-73479bd410a825131ce793eadfa4ae04_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1183' height='767'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"1183\" data-rawheight=\"767\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-99068679309ad3dcb226ec1d1c55865a\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b1e2b5f140b1b0eca2932b0ac8c90d2b_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1183\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-73479bd410a825131ce793eadfa4ae04_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-73479bd410a825131ce793eadfa4ae04_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"vgSAqmW2\"><b>4、<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=600608634&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%9D%9C%E6%B0%8F%E8%82%8C%E8%90%A5%E5%85%BB%E4%B8%8D%E8%89%AF&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">杜氏肌营养不良<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，关联基因DMD，XL遗传方式</b></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-74bb03b143fc0e50f0f3c18ce446a5ad_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"280\" data-rawheight=\"233\" data-size=\"small\" data-original-token=\"v2-4a6d48169f4bd64417104173c6f0c506\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a862e646833f4d6ccba7d6879dff2062_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"280\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='280' height='233'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"280\" data-rawheight=\"233\" data-size=\"small\" data-original-token=\"v2-4a6d48169f4bd64417104173c6f0c506\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-a862e646833f4d6ccba7d6879dff2062_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"280\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-74bb03b143fc0e50f0f3c18ce446a5ad_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"emCM6xKB\">杜氏肌营养不良（DMD）是最常见的一类进行性肌营养不良，本病特点为<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=600608634&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E8%BF%9B%E8%A1%8C%E6%80%A7%E8%82%8C%E8%90%8E%E7%BC%A9&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">进行性肌萎缩<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，预后差。<b>DMD患儿双侧腓肠肌逐渐呈假性肥大、腱反射减弱或消失、近端肌无力导致的行走困难。随着病情加重，约在12岁前丧失行走能力，20岁左右死于呼吸衰竭或心力衰竭。</b></p><p data-pid=\"1UqsnTWg\">DMD呈<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=600608634&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=X-%E8%BF%9E%E9%94%81%E9%9A%90%E6%80%A7%E9%81%97%E4%BC%A0&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">X-连锁隐性遗传<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，目前已知的致病基因为<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=600608634&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=DMD%E5%9F%BA%E5%9B%A0&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">DMD基因<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，其中约60%-70%为1个或多个外显子的缺失突变，约5%-10%为重复突变，另有约25%-35%为点突变（<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=600608634&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%8D%95%E7%A2%B1%E5%9F%BA%E7%AA%81%E5%8F%98&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">单碱基突变<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>及小的碱基插入缺失突变）。有1/3病例为散发，没有家族史，是由新发生的基因突变（de novo）造成的。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b4680ba38e96e44b8e4a749d6919109e_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1179\" data-rawheight=\"836\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-d32faf7a4e9e3c1088639523732f3692\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e0db587cd6d7ddc198ca7a9699af83ca_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1179\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b4680ba38e96e44b8e4a749d6919109e_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1179' height='836'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"1179\" data-rawheight=\"836\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-d32faf7a4e9e3c1088639523732f3692\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e0db587cd6d7ddc198ca7a9699af83ca_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1179\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b4680ba38e96e44b8e4a749d6919109e_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b4680ba38e96e44b8e4a749d6919109e_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div><figcaption>部分突变位点</figcaption></figure><p data-pid=\"Aa-cgYVA\">DMD发病率为约1/3500 新生男婴，BMD发病率为约1/18450新生男婴。<b>患者主要为男性</b>，部分女性携带者受<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=600608634&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=X%E6%9F%93%E8%89%B2%E4%BD%93&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">X染色体<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>部分失活模式的影响而出现部分病症。</p><p data-pid=\"Do6I8c8T\">……</p><p data-pid=\"qSeu5QoF\"><b>还有SGCG等等</b></p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
  "excerpt": "为了能好好回答这个问题，我特地查了很多资料给你找来几种多数为男性患者的严重疾病：\n\n1、X连锁肩胛腓骨肌病，关联基因FHL1，XL遗传方式\n\n依靠轮椅生活\n\nX连锁肩胛腓骨肌病是一种进行性肌病，临床表现为进行性肌无力和萎缩、上下肢无力、足下垂、翼状肩胛，肌肉活检可见肌病病变。大部分患者失去独立行走能力，必须依靠轮椅生活。\n\n部分突变位点\n\n2、X连锁原卟啉病，关联基因ALAS2，XL遗传\n\nX连锁原卟啉病（XLP）是一种X连锁遗传的卟啉病，男性患者的临床表现为皮肤光敏感性，通常从婴儿期或幼儿期开始发病。\n\n患者在光照下几分钟就会感到皮肤刺痛、火辣、疼痛以及瘙痒，并可能伴有发红、肿胀。光毒性反应",
